name: mist mover
description:
according to folklore, rudimentary molecule automation systems allowed technomancers to control the properties of water particles. vast blankets of fog were occasionally conjured at gatherings during special moments, immersing spectators in an ocean of refracted visual phenomenon. 

cast to invoke mystique. inscribed by tenorless circa 2022 // elements collection [water]

one of three artifacts from technomancy beta test 0.1
